<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6683206>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ibityraboia caraguata sp. nov., holotype male. A: habitus, dorsal view; B: head, frontal view; C: head and pronotum, dorsal view; D: head and pronotum, lateral view; E: Thoracic sternites, ventral view; F: foreleg, lateral view; G: midleg, lateral view; H: hindleg, lateral view; I–J: Terminalia in ventral and dorsal view respectively; K: Apex of cerci, dorsal view. Abbreviations: Mes: mesobasisternum; Met: metabasisternum; Cer: cerci; Sty: styli; Pl: subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6683206/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6683212>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Ibityraboia caraguata sp. nov., left tegmina of male in dorsal view. Abbreviations: AP: Posterior anal vein; AA: anterior anal vein; CuA: anterior cubital vein; CuP: posterior cubital vein; MA: anterior median vein; MP: posterior median vein; R: radial vein; Sc: subcostal vein." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6683212/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6683220>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Ibityraboia caraguata sp. nov., male internal genitalia. A–B: phallus, ventral view; C–D: phallus, dorsal view; E: phallus with titillator sclerite, ventral view; F: titillator sclerite. Abbreviations: AP: sclerites of apodemes; DF: dorsal fold; DL: dorsal lobe(s); EV: ejaculatory vesicles; TS: titillator sclerite; TI: titillator process; Lw. vl.: lower folds of ventral lobe; Up. vl.: upper folds of ventral lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6683220/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6683204>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pictorial key to differentiate the genera Copiphora and Ibityraboia gen. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6683204/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

